<h1>If-Else Statement</h1>

<p>In certain cases, it may not be necessary to execute all statements in the script.
<br>
With If-Else statement, users have the choice of conditional execution to avoid wasting cycles on some very expensive lines that may not be necessary in some cases.
<br>
Below we have the method to use the if-else statement
